# PLAYER::REMOVE_PLAYER_TARGETABLE_ENTITY

## Summary
Remove entity added to targetable array via ADD_PLAYER_TARGETABLE_ENTITY

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player
* **ENTITY_INDEX** target
